Package com.werdpressed.partisan.rundo

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RunDo
    RunDo implementations monitor and manipulate EditText fields, by periodically saving snippets of text to Collections and reinstating them through RunDo.undo() and RunDo.redo() calls.
    RunDo.Callbacks
    Implement to receive callbacks whenever RunDo.undo() or RunDo.redo() methods are called
    RunDo.TextLink
    Used byRunDo implementations to establish a link with an EditText
    WriteToArrayDeque  
  • Class Summary

    FixedSizeArrayDeque<T>
    Implementation of ArrayDeque class that adds a fixed, maximum capacity.
    RunDo.Factory
    Returns a RunDo implementation which extends either Fragment or Fragment.
    RunDoNative
    Implementation of RunDo which extends Fragment.
    RunDoSupport
    Implementation of RunDo which extends Fragment.
    SubtractStrings  
    SubtractStrings.Item
    Model class which encapsulates all important pieces of information relating to the differences between two Strings, calculated by SubtractStrings
